{"tid":1615511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌曬你哋班連登仔老母，你哋班仆街恩將仇報","createTime":"2019-10-03T06:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T12:41:50.000Z","uid":298001,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac50815c2331285720f83de167b6b3f742d4975","tid":1615511,"uid":298001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"大家發夢有鋪頭收留大家，我明白手足真係好多謝佢哋，好想揚岀去等大家知道，然後可以大大力用錢懲罰佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n對住小店咁做，真係無問題。<br />\n但係如果嗰啲係大集團旗下嘅鋪頭，請大家小心，要讚揚都唔好放上網揚岀去。<br />\n<br />\n因為你永遠唔知道，大集團會唔會因為咁就cut佢租約，又或者老闆/高層會唔會炒咗幫過手足嘅員工。亦可能係入面員工可能係暪住自己老闆去幫你。<br />\n<br />\n你地唔好唔記得大部分店有cctv，到時有搜查令員工係冇得唔比，咁到時裡面所有人就會攬炒！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家再係到爆走難時間鋪頭幫過自己，繼續講去咗邊到邊到走難，你哋會累死自己！！！都會累死入面既員工！！！<br />\n<br />\n鋪頭員工比人清算你對唔對得住人，你哋班連登仔就話冇仔女，人哋分分鐘成頭家要養。以後就無人可以再幫到你哋！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋班連登仔係咪想搞到人無左份工，仲要有風險咩條例協助他人犯法？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n d人唔好再爆秘密得唔得. 做人要有道義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278fccaea8a17f4905657ddf47b76f3358c84877","tid":1615511,"uid":275677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d857029fe1db3652ca121bba62102ac08baffeb","tid":1615511,"uid":75668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f